metadata.name: Khilanmarg
metadata.description:
Khilanmarg 6km away from Gulmarg, Khilanmarg is a riveting natural meadow which offers a splendid unparalleled panoramic view of the Himalayan range including the Nanga Parbat. A favourite destination of tourists, during spring it is a spectacular landscape engulfed with vibrant blossoming flowers and in winters, itâ€™s one of the ski runs popular with skiing enthusiasts.

(taken on 15jan 2023)
